%% Traversal is a recursive `match` on the enum. Every algorithm over
%% the composite follows the same shape.
flowchart TD
    Call[".total_size(&root)"]
    Call --> Match{match node}
    Match -->|File { bytes }| Leaf["bytes"]
    Match -->|Folder { children }| Recurse["children.iter()<br/>.map(total_size)<br/>.sum()"]
    Recurse --> Call
